57
00:03:49,400 --> 00:03:50,220
- Neboj sa, len choď.
- Dobre.

58
00:03:50,220 --> 00:03:51,740
- Tak idem.
- Maj sa.

59
00:03:54,140 --> 00:03:55,660
- Chen Qing Qing.
- Hm?

60
00:04:05,620 --> 00:04:08,060
Lin Yi Yang pripustil svoje chyby,

61
00:04:08,340 --> 00:04:10,000
