67
00:04:34,540 --> 00:04:36,220
Umri, Si Tu Feng!

68
00:04:36,600 --> 00:04:38,940
- Kde smrdia?
- Naozaj smrdia.

69
00:04:39,240 --> 00:04:40,060
Dobre.

70
00:04:40,440 --> 00:04:42,380
Tým si buď istý. Zabudol si?

71
