114
00:06:43,240 --> 00:06:45,540
Prezidentka Wang, vy... Toto... Toto je...

115
00:06:46,360 --> 00:06:47,400
Prezidentka Wang,

116
00:06:48,100 --> 00:06:49,040
prijímam to.

117
00:06:49,860 --> 00:06:51,040
Hej, Si Tu Feng.

118
00:06:53,530 --> 00:06:54,930
Xiao Feng to povedal.

119
00:06:55,340 --> 00:06:56,920
Takže si počkám a uvidím.

120
