332
00:19:44,240 --> 00:19:45,680
Ešte ale neotváraj oči.

333
00:19:50,380 --> 00:19:51,380
Neotváraj oči.

334
00:19:56,860 --> 00:19:57,860
Si Tu Feng!

335
00:19:58,280 --> 00:20:00,100
Už môžeš otvoriť oči!

336
00:20:15,400 --> 00:20:16,060
Si Tu Feng,

337
00:20:16,620 --> 00:20:17,620
